    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. but i've been reading a lot about how it's actually a pretty critical part of meeting climate goals. like, if cities dont do this, they basically can't hit their carbon reduction targets. do you think it's possible to implement these kinds of things without just focusing on the economic complaints?",
